{"author":{"id":"ae924cad0eccd510bd7c1844896b3dcc00e7daa039003bd9719a515e70528ab9"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1761763636,"nonce":"ybPclMfpAQ6ad/22XnbmKxWmabU=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOAW4Y0s7UoiU0","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/7410","origin":"github"},"title":"Configure MAF tools to use local file caching","message":"## Description\n\nMAF tools currently attempt to fetch data from UCSC servers, causing performance issues and instability. Need to configure tools to use locally cached MAF and 2bit files instead of remote network access.\n\n## Problem\n\nCurrent setup uses `gbdbLoc1=http://hgdownload.soe.ucsc.edu/gbdb/` in hg.conf, which causes:\n- Slow performance due to network I/O\n- Failures and timeouts when fetching large files\n- Dependency on UCSC download server availability\n- UCSC download server not designed for real-time tool usage\n- Excessive load on UCSC infrastructure\n\n## Impact\n\nFrom email with Brian Raney (UCSC):\n\u003e \"It probably would be good for y'all to mirror files in /gbdb locally and then unset gbdbLoc1 in your hg.conf. I don't know if this has been discussed or not. It's probably not a good idea for y'all to be accessing all the bigBed and twoBit files in that directory through our download server, which is designed for bulk download.\"\n\n## Solution Approach\n\n1. Remove GBDB entry from hg.conf file\n2. Mirror necessary files from /gbdb locally\n3. Point to local genome files (e.g., sacCer3.2bit)\n4. Set up local caching infrastructure for MAF files (@natefoo knows about this)\n5. Update tool wrappers to use local paths\n\n## Configuration Changes Needed\n\n**Current hg.conf:**\n```\ndb.host=genome-euro-mysql.soe.ucsc.edu\ndb.user=genomep\ndb.password=password\ncentral.db=hgcentral\ncentral.host=genome-euro-mysql.soe.ucsc.edu\ncentral.user=genomep\ncentral.password=password\ngbdbLoc1=http://hgdownload.soe.ucsc.edu/gbdb/\nforceTwoBit=on\n```\n\n**Updated hg.conf:**\n```\ndb.host=genome-euro-mysql.soe.ucsc.edu\ndb.user=genomep\ndb.password=password\ncentral.db=hgcentral\ncentral.host=genome-euro-mysql.soe.ucsc.edu\ncentral.user=genomep\ncentral.password=password\n# gbdbLoc1 removed - use local files instead\nforceTwoBit=on\n```\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] Remove GBDB entry from hd.conf file\n- [ ] Identify required 2bit files for priority genomes\n- [ ] Mirror 2bit files to local Galaxy storage (or CVMFS)\n- [ ] Point tools to local sacCer3.2bit file (and others as needed)\n- [ ] Set up local caching infrastructure for MAF files\n- [ ] Update hg.conf to use local files instead of remote URLs\n- [ ] Document configuration approach for other genomes\n- [ ] Test performance improvement vs remote access\n- [ ] Create maintenance plan for keeping local files updated\n\n\n- Related to Issue #7409","files":null}]}